<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hǎo shí guāng 迦南358</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 hǎo shí guāng hǎo shí guāng mò ràng nà shí guāng suí zhe liú shuǐ tǎng.
 nǐ zài zǒu wǒ zài zǒu suǒ yǐ lù cái huì xiū de nà me zhǎng.
 zhǎng zhǎng de lù a xiàng hé fāng, zhǎng zhǎng de lù a tōng jiā xiāng,
 tú jìng jiā lì lì bó dà ní cūn zhuāng, hái zǒu xī ān de dà dào shàng
 dà dào shàng de zi mín yī lù gē chàng xǐ yáng yáng,
 jué wàng rén huǐ gǎi zhǔ fǔ píng chuàng shāng, zhǔ yào zhāo jù wàn guó wàn bāng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>358</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>